{"tid":616894,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"What we can do for Hong Kong","createTime":"2018-04-04T14:22:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-04T16:43:39.000Z","uid":94620,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"72852a116e9217395769f9fe48e7d79c3a355d73","tid":616894,"uid":94620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T14:22:18.000Z","msg":"好開心見到最近連登多咗人講政治<br />\n名校secret收皮都證明咗其實我地係有力量去改變現況 即使微不足道<br />\n香港冇一個政治領袖 加上呢幾年嚟產生嘅政治無力感 令到我地更加消極<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n但係我相信 至少我地可以做到呢幾樣野：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">教育</span></span><br />\n每個人都可以參與 就算唔係教育工作者<br />\n而家政治做緊嘅野就係透過社教化潛移默化地向下一代洗腦 做得非常成功<br />\n而我地要做嘅係對抗呢個意識形態<br />\n向學生同新一代宣揚本土文化<br />\n作為老師嘅你，可以向學生講多少少政治<br />\n令到佢地留意多d時事 <br />\n迫佢地寫多d繁體字 教佢地正確嘅歷史<br />\n作為家長嘅你，家庭對小朋友嘅影響非常大<br />\n未必要將自己嘅立場套係佢身上<br />\n但一定要培養佢地思考能力 仲有對社會政治嘅觸覺<br />\n唔好好似港豬廢老咁隨波逐流<br />\n如果你同我一樣係個廢青，亦都唔係咩都做唔到<br />\n要堅守自己信念唔好動搖 知道咩係公義<br />\n得閒同屋企人朋友講下政治 要知道輿論嘅力量係非常強大<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">網絡</span></span><br />\n呢樣野唔使點講<br />\n八成連登仔都係鍵盤戰士<br />\n互聯網嘅影響力係非常大<br />\n基本上你既一言一行 都會影響腦荀都未生齊嘅小學雞<br />\n所以港共先要洗咁多錢養班五毛<br />\n對於唔公義嘅事千其唔好手軟<br />\n要狙擊到底 就係一個正評負評<br />\n都會有連鎖效應<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">記住 我地要奪取話語權</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">個人</span></span><br />\n個人方面做到嘅野好多<br />\n第一當然係要擁護本土文化<br />\n要有原則 例如唔好寫簡體字 <br />\n第二係行使公民責任<br />\n就算係投白票廢票都好 都要去投票<br />\n唔投票就等於放棄咗最基本最僅餘嘅個人權利<br />\n最後一樣都係最難做到<br />\n就係個人修養 <br />\n睇多d書 當有朝一日有人challenge你嘅時候都有理有據 令到人信服<br />\n另外就係要證明自己同班冇文化嘅建制廢老唔係同一個水平 令到下一代知道邊個先係代表真理公義<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">到最後最重要最重要嘅係勿忘初衷<br />\n我知道條路會好難行 <br />\n好多人都會為眼前嘅利益誘惑<br />\n為五斗米折腰<br />\n或者日復日厭倦政治 甚至潛移默化地認為一切係理所當然 <br />\n但係我相信 香港嘅未來其實係掌握係我地手上</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0017d9ca61afe1bf791e7123bbd48fccfc4940f0","tid":616894,"uid":18948,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T14:23:11.000Z","msg":"What can we do for Hong Kong <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da45d2c96cfd1137af5db9d0ca4ccff5fa8c4bec","tid":616894,"uid":163350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T14:23:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"eb9952004e632d4746151be9518c0c709055e966","tid":616894,"uid":94620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da45d2c96cfd1137af5db9d0ca4ccff5fa8c4bec","tid":616894,"uid":163350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T14:23:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T15:24:34.000Z","msg":"我地係打緊仗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75baff5d230a1cd0520b883875fe4f383dcfce64","tid":616894,"uid":103127,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T15:28:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"746b4b888492e2b99b6776e1a3bc8790a1a11997","tid":616894,"uid":103127,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T15:30:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5e1562928af7692bebb895215acf1573a7a97f90","tid":616894,"uid":7840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T15:31:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"382479aa75f5e2c9fbe16f2fc85da90cedcc4c85","tid":616894,"uid":5843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T15:31:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02d1607eccfa23c32327dca6cac6e78522a68638","tid":616894,"uid":103127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T15:37:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8743b569af1674e1e582343926dafb69119ba9ad","tid":616894,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"75baff5d230a1cd0520b883875fe4f383dcfce64","tid":616894,"uid":103127,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T15:28:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T15:40:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五毛人見人愛</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/04/234020_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F04%2F234020_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=348e2c64&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"da39489701137a0bcbf2c1d7ec67b489e0bcae2d","tid":616894,"uid":37375,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T15:42:33.000Z","msg":"leave this city."},{"pid":"07972ae57553e1a6c22366608a4bb95c216e1465","tid":616894,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T15:49:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"091c0616c659b81cad7a59a3cb1b64be3ee5fd58","tid":616894,"uid":94620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da39489701137a0bcbf2c1d7ec67b489e0bcae2d","tid":616894,"uid":37375,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T15:42:33.000Z","msg":"leave this city."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T15:50:03.000Z","msg":"個個都話想走<br />\n又有幾多人走到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n既然走唔到 就諗辦法去改變"},{"pid":"42f330414fa39e67c456e89ae299aa83f942dc5c","tid":616894,"uid":37375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"091c0616c659b81cad7a59a3cb1b64be3ee5fd58","tid":616894,"uid":94620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da39489701137a0bcbf2c1d7ec67b489e0bcae2d","tid":616894,"uid":37375,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T15:42:33.000Z","msg":"leave this city."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T15:50:03.000Z","msg":"個個都話想走<br />\n又有幾多人走到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n既然走唔到 就諗辦法去改變"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T1